oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Greenway flooding
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Thompson Brothers
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Flooded area near Greenway, Knox County, TN. November 18, 1935. Ordered by James G. Johnson, County Attorney. The flooding was possibly the result of very heavy rain on November 13, 1935. The photos were possibly taken at Greenway Rd, Knox County, near Fountain City.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Floods;
